AETHERMUD APPRENTICE WIZARD

position: apprentice
wiz_role: apprentice
who tag: [Apprentice]

Apprentices are temporary wizards created by makewiz. They get a workroom,
basic ambassador-level file tools, and an apprentice kit.

TOOL: kit (also: apprentice)
  1. Choose track: rp / domain / coding
  2. View task brief
  3. Draft / edit submission
  4. Submit to domain queue
  5. View status (including ready_for_setrole)

TRACK TASKS
  RP     - Campaign/quest proposal -> domain review -> coding queue
  Domain - Area outline -> domain approve -> ready for setrole
  Coding - Realm room+NPC paths -> domain review -> coding check

WHAT YOU CAN DO
  - workroom, kit
  - ed / cat / ls (ambassador path)
  - cre channel
  - read the reference book in your workroom

WHAT YOU CANNOT DO YET
  - QCS build (needs coding + staff of creation)
  - domain tools (staff of domains)
  - RP skill / tattoo tools
  - admin commands (update, warmboot, setrole, etc.)

PROMOTION
When domain/coding mark you ready, an admin still runs:

  setrole <you> <admin|domain|coding|rp>

See also: help kit, help makewiz, help setrole, help staff *wizard staff
